\id 2JN - Fore NT [for] -Papua New Guinea 1974 (web version -2013) 
\h 2 Yoni 
\toc1 Yoni Ma Nkisa Kaentiye (Tara Yagane) 
\toc2 2 Yoni 
\toc3 2Yo 
\mt1 YONI MA NKISA KAENTIYE (TARA YAGANE)  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Naeba monota kabiyo ntagaramana, Koti ugatanti nkwae'makake yagaragakeri naeba ma nkisapa kaeyuwe. Piya, naeba taga kamanaka napima tigeka nabugaye. We, nae nabinto wanane. A'ya'ma taga kamana abibebe pe kina'miba, igeba kaga tigeka ibugaye.  
\v 2 Piya, taga kamana'amaba ibaba taeti waintana, taeti waima waiyaba mikibika napima piyama yune.  
\v 3 Pigoya, Koti tabage, Isu Karaisiti taba ntagarabe, isigeba tagantana puma agu kao'ena puratamaginisi, isigetisa awagaenabe, isintara'enabe, paruyenabe taeti waima waiyeno.   
\s1 Agu kao'enama kamanane  
\p
\v 4 Pigoya, ka'isa yagaragampigi tabarempa utarataisa puma tagantanaba aegaraka, naeba abima tabera na'mu puwe.  
\v 5 We, ma nkwae, ago kamanapa kapa kaema ugamuwe. Pipa kasa kamana kanta puma wanane. Paitaka'ya uramintanaga mayama ugamuwe: Taeba tao'mipa agu kao'ena puwaitanoma, yuwe.  
\v 6 Piya, paitaka'ya: Agu kao'enama ki'i waiyoma, Kotiba yogiri abintane. Piya, taeba unti kamana'wapa aegarakubompepa, taeba agu kao'ena pukenaenama nkagoba pukune.   
\s1 Kumpari kina'mi kamanane  
\p
\v 7 Pigoya, uwaena timiyo pikena kina'miba mampabinti nasewe. Igeba: Isu Karaisitiba au'yaga kampa aborantine, yewe. Piya kina'miba igeba timiyo puma Karaisiti kama kina'ena potawe.  
\v 8 We, tigeba titipa aogima kabiyiyo. Tigeba mono yugama nkau'wa kaisanaga kabima mima, aogi ika mpaekenaga aobi piyo.  
\v 9 Piya, ka'waina aeba Karaisiti kamanati kampa atokaenta atate to ki'i wakibipa, Kotiba aegeba kampa mikiye. Piya, to ka'waina aeba Karaisiti kamanati atokaeyakanaba, tababe yagarawampabe kaga aege mikibewe.  
\v 10 Piya, ka'waina aeba Karaisiti au'yaga aboranti kamana'nane. To kamana urite nasima tigeti uma irosakiripa, tigeba wa'eritapa a-nkababuma, kayonenaba a-potaiyo.  
\v 11 Piya, kayonena potakibi'naba, aeba agunta yugawa ao'maekiye.   
\s1 Nagarikena kamanane  
\p
\v 12 Pigoya, urimikena kamana'nepa uwaena waintegi, naeba esapi kaesanagaba kampa nabegi, tigeti waka, nawamupisa uma abenema, yuwe. Piya pekana, ta'muntanarepa anosakiye.   
\p
\v 13 Pigoya, Koti otanti ka'nanto ntagaramiba: Aya pene, ugatawe.  
\q1 Yoni piya isa kaentiye.   